00:35:37,294 --> 00:35:42,096
playing your five-hour game for over and over using different play styles and making sure

485
00:35:42,156 --> 00:35:45,958
that they have the consistent emotion throughout.

486
00:35:46,078 --> 00:35:48,479
It's very hard, if not impossible task.

487
00:35:49,629 --> 00:35:56,999
Now, instead I think, as I said, that we should see this as something that is just part that improves the experience.

488
00:35:57,019 --> 00:35:58,280
Think about game graphics.

489
00:35:58,701 --> 00:36:04,949
