490
00:36:05,009 --> 00:36:07,932
and then as we have progressed, we're getting better and better and better.

491
00:36:08,533 --> 00:36:14,175
sort of game graphics, where at this moment we have all these graphics and pretty much none of it

492
00:36:14,355 --> 00:36:18,097
directly has anything to do with the core of the game.

493
00:36:18,397 --> 00:36:23,680
And I think that game mechanics can play the same part, that they don't have to be part of the core game,

494
00:36:23,940 --> 00:36:27,521
but they can just enhance the experience in some way for us.

